quran[27]{c,v,t}:
  17,23,Aur tera perwerdigar saaf saaf hukum dey chuka hai kay tum uss kay siwa kissi aur ki ibadat na kerna aur maa baap kay sath ehsan kerna. Agar teri mojoodgi mein inn mein say aik ya yeh dono burhapay ko phonch jayen to unn kay aagay uff tak na kehna na unhen daant dapat kerna bulkay unn kay sath adab-o-ehtram say baat cheet kerna
  17,24,Aur aajzi aur mohabbat kay sath unn kay samney tawazo ka bazoo pust rakhay rakhna aur dua kertay rehna kay aey meray perwerdigar! Inn per waisa hi reham ker jaisa enhon ney meray bachpan mein meri perwerish ki hai
  17,25,Jo kuch tumharay dilon mein hai ussay tumhara rab bakhoobi janta hai agar tum nek ho to woh to tujoo kerney walon ko bakhshney wala hai
  17,26,Aur rishtay daaron ka aur miskeenon aur musafiron ka haq ada kertay raho aur israaf aur bey jaa kharch say bacho
  17,27,Bey jaa kharch kerney walay shetano kay bhai hain. Aur shetan apney perwerdigar ka bara hi na shukra hai
  17,28,Aur agar tujhay inn say mun pher lena paray apney rab ki iss rehmat ki justujoo mein jiss ki tu umeed rakhta hai to bhi tujhay chahiye kay umdagi aur narmi say unhen samjha dey
  17,29,Apna hath apni gardan say bandha hua na rakh aur na ussay bilkul hi khol dey kay phir malamat kiya hua dar manda beth jaye
  17,30,Yaqeenan tera rab jiss kay liye chahaye rozi kushada ker deta hai aur jiss kay liye chahaye tang. Yaqeenan woh apney bandon say baa khabar aur khoob dekhney wala hai
  17,31,Aur muflisi kay khof say apni aulado ko naa maar dalo unn ko aur tum ko hum rozi detay hain . yaqeenan inn ka qatal kerna kabeera gunah hai
  17,32,Khabrdaar zinna kay qareeb bhi na phatakna kiyon kay woh bari bey hayaee hai aur boht hi buri raah hai
  17,33,Aur kissi jaan ko jiss ka maarna Allah ney haram ker diya hai hergiz na haq qatal na kerna aur jo shaks mazloom honey ki soorat mein maar dala jaye hum ney uss kay waris ko taqat dey rakhi hai pus ussay chahiye kay maar dalney mein ziyadti na keray be-shak woh madad kiya gaya hai
  17,34,Aur yateem kay maal kay qareeb bhi na jao ba-juz uss tareeqay kay jo boht hi behtar ho yahan tak kay woh apni balooghat ko phonch jaye aur waday pooray kero kiyon kay qol-o-qarar ki baaz purs honey wali hai
  17,35,Aur jab naapney lago to bharpoor paymaney say naapo aur seedhi tarazoo say tola kero. Yehi behtar hai aur anjam kay lehaz say bhi boht acha hai
  17,36,Jiss baat ki tujhay khabar hi na ho uss kay peechay mat parr. Kiyon kaan aur aankh aur dil inn mein say her aik say pooch gooch ki janey wali hai
  17,37,Aur zamin mein akar ker na chal kay na to tu zamin ko phaar sakta hai aur na lambai mein paharon ko phonch sakta hai
  17,38,Inn sab kaamon ki buraee teray rab kay nazdeek (sakht) na pasand hai
  17,39,Yeh bhi munjmila uss wahee kay hai jo teri janib teray rab ney hikmat say utari hai tu Allah kay sath kissi aur ko mabood na banana kay malamat khorda aur raand-e-dargah hoker dozakh mein daal diya jaye
  17,40,Kiya beton kay liye to Allah ney tumhen chant liya aur khud apney liye farishton ko larkiyan bana lin? Be-shak tum boht bara bol bol rahey ho
  17,41,Hum ney to iss quran mein her her tarah biyan farma diya kay log samajh jayen lekin iss say enhen to nafrat hi barhti hai
  17,42,Keh dijiye! Kay Allah kay siwa aur mabood bhi hotay jaisay kay yeh log kehtay hain to zaroor woh abb tak malik-e-arsh ki janib raah dhoond nikaltay
  17,43,Jo kuch yeh kehtay hain iss say woh pak aur bala tar boht door aur boht buland hai
  17,44,Saton aasman aur zamin aur jo bhi inn mein hai ussi ki tasbeeh ker rahey hain. Aisi koi cheez nahi jo ussay pakeezgi aur tareef kay sath yaad na kerti ho.haan yeh sahih hai kay tum uss ki tasbeeh samajh nahi saktay. Woh bara burbaar aur bakhshney wala hai
  17,45,Tu jab quran parhta hai hum teray aur unn logon kay darmiyan jo aakhirat per yaqeen nahi rakhtay aik posheeda hijab daal detay hain
  17,46,Aur inn kay dilon per hum ney pardey daal diye hain kay woh issay samjhen aur inn kay kano mein bojh aur jab tu sirf Allah hi ka zikar uss ki toheed kay sath iss quran mein kerta hai to woh roo gardani kertay peeth pher ker bhag kharay hotay hain
  17,47,Jiss gharz say woh log issay suntay hain unn (ki niyaton) say hum khoob aagah hain jab yeh aap ki taraf kaan lagaye huye hotay hain tab bhi aur yeh mashwara kertay hain tab bhi jab kay zalim kehtay hain kay tum uss ki tabeydaari mein lagay huye ho jin per jadoo ker diya gaya hai
  17,48,Dekhen to sahih aap kay liye kiya kiya misalen biyan kertay hain pus woh behak rahey hain. Abb to raah pana inn kay bus mein nahi raha
  17,49,Enhon ney kaha kay kiya jab hum haddiyan aur (mitti hoker) reza reza hojayen gay to kiya hum azz sir-e-no peda ker kay phir doobara utha kharay kerdiye jayen gay